metadata.name: Comebackids
metadata.description: Comebackids is more than the lore; it's a story with a rich history in the art of hustle. 2D narrative PFP digital art with utility that will serve as the heart of this project in return providing longevity and sustainability for our community. Our story is something most all of us can relate to giving the last few years whether it be a bad investment, a loss job, or anything else that has caused hardships in your life, but more importantly we focus on the comeback because it's always stronger than the setbacks and the best is yet to come!
